<translate> <!--T:5--> '''Camera Drone''' is a [[Special:MyLanguage/Camera |Camera]] feature, exclusive to [[VRChat+|VRC+]]. It serves as a fully-functional [[wikipedia:unmanned aerial vehicle|drone]] that you can pilot within VRChat, either for recording purposes, or simply to fly around and have fun with friends.</translate>

<translate> <!--T:6--> You can find the Camera Drone in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu |Quick Menu]] under the Camera tab, and clicking '''Launch Drone'''.</translate>

<translate> ==Settings== <!--T:7--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:8-->
*Take Photo
*Enable FPV (first-person view)
*Self Leveling: On, Off
*Respawn
*Spout Stream: On, Off
* Focus
*Mask
*Filters
*Photo Resolution
*Stream Resolution
*Grid: On, Off</translate>
<translate> ===Presets=== <!--T:9--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:10-->
In this menu, you can choose a preset for your drone's flight:
* Micro
*Cinematic
*Racing
*Freestyle</translate>
<translate> <!--T:11-->
Additionally, you can customize your drone's flight, using the following sliders:
*Motor Power: 2.0-12.0
*Drone Drag: 0.50-1.50
*Drone Cross Section Area: 0.010-0.050
*Drone Mass: 0.10-0.25
*Camera Tilt: 0.0-70.0
*Pitch Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Roll Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Yaw Rate: 100.0-1000.0
*Throttle Rate: 0.25-1.00
*Pitch Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Roll Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Yaw Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Throttle Expo: 0.00-1.00
*Pitch Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Roll Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Yaw Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Throttle Center Sensitivity: 1.0-1000.0
*Self-Leveling Max Angle: 10.0-45.0
*Mode Change Smoothing: 0.0-1.00 </translate>

<translate> ===Controller settings === <!--T:12--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:13--> Control Schemes: 1 (Pitch, Yaw), 2 (Throttle, Yaw), 3 (Pitch, Roll), 4 (Throttle, Roll)</translate>

<translate> <!--T:14--> Inversion: On, Off</translate>

<translate> <!--T:15--> Dead Zone: 0.00-1.00 (adjustable by increasing or decreasing the dead zone by 0.01 at a time)</translate>
<translate> ====Desktop controls==== <!--T:16--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:17-->
Mouse Mode: Continuous, Relative

<!--T:44-->
Mouse Sensitivity: 0.1-10.0 (adjustable by increasing or decreasing the slider by 0.1 at a time)

<!--T:45-->
Mouse Relative Rate: 1.0-100.0 (adjustable by increasing or decreasing the slider)

<!--T:46-->
Mouse Relative Curve: 1.0-100.0 (adjustable by increasing or decreasing the slider)

<!--T:47-->
Mouse Power Curve: 1.0-3.0 (adjustable by increasing or decreasing the slider by 0.1 at a time)</translate>

<translate> == Customization == <!--T:18--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:19--> The drone and its colors can be customized in the "Cosmetics" tab in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory |Inventory]]. "Customize" button is also available directly in the Drone Camera.</translate>

<translate> <!--T:20--> Color palette options include: Primary, Secondary and Trail.</translate>

