<translate> ==Additional information== <!--T:36--></translate>
<translate> <!--T:37--> Not comfortable with flying? No problem! The Camera Drone has various control and flight settings that let you adjust how it handles, ensuring that newcomers and experienced pilots alike can enjoy flying it.</translate>

<translate> <!--T:38--> ''Tip: We're seeking scenic worlds with accurate colliders for ideal flying experiences. If you have any suggestions, share them on social media with #VRCDrone!''</translate>

